#. type: Plain text
#: HandBook.adoc:1655
#
msgid ""
"These key bindings (for US keyboard layout) don't need a numeric keypad.  If "
"you have one, use the <<desktop_keys,speakup desktop keys>> easier to use, "
"especially if you use another keyboard layout than US."
